<article id="post-574" class="post-574 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-trains category-travel tag-around-the-world tag-china tag-hong-kong">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/06/ode-to-hong-kong-trolleys/" rel="bookmark">Ode to Hong Kong Trolleys</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Trolley headlight burning bright,<br />
cart me through this stormy night,<br />
Away to the curious city sights<br />
And let me view the highest heights!<br />
Trolley, tram, whatever they say<br />
You run &#8217;round the city every day<br />
100 years and one you tramp away<br />
So darn cute, promise me you&#8217;ll stay?<br />
<a><br />
<img src="http://www.howtogetlost.com/media/DSC03688.JPG" alt="Hong Kong trolleys" width="300" /><br />
</a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
