<article id="post-542" class="post-542 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-trains category-travel tag-around-the-world">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/05/cough/" rel="bookmark">Cough</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I&#8217;m sick. I caught Amy&#8217;s cold.<br />
I hate being sick.<br />
The only thing worse than being sick is being sick on a train. It ruins the experience.<br />
Blech.<br />
<em>Sniff</em></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

